data.description: Welcome to this Wonderful Traditional home in desirable Bella Vista, a fantastic location just off of Potranco Rd. The home, built by Highland Homes, sits on an oversized cul-de-sac lot and offers 4 bedrooms, 2 and one half bathrooms and has been beautifully updated with attractive quality finishes. A half bathroom, utility room and a private office or additional living/dining room downstairs make this an ideal floor plan with ultimate flexibility. The island kitchen with solid countertops and a gas cooktop looks out to the family room that is anchored by a gorgeous stone fireplace. The eat in kitchen provides multiple dining areas with an adjoining breakfast room and a breakfast bar at the kitchen island. Custom cabinetry offers abundant storage in the Kitchen, laundry room and bathroms. The recently updated wood-look tile flooring runs throughout the main living and dining spaces of the home. The large primary suite is located on the main level featuring an expansive walk in shower, dual vanities and large walk in closet. An additional 3 bedrooms and one full bathroom are located upstairs. The backyard has endless potential with a raised bed garden area showcasing a lovely grapevine and room for more of your favorite plantings. The updates to this property are not only cosmetic, but are also updates to some of the major systems to include the roof and gutters.  2 car garage. Dog doors. Fully fenced yard. *NEW ROOF AND GUTTERS IN 2021,NEW HVAC IN 2023 AND 2017. STUNNING MASTER BATHROOM REMODEL. WALKING DISTANCE TO ELEMENTARY AND MIDDLE SCHOOLS. COMMUNITY POOL, PLAYGROUND AND BASKETBALL COURTS.*
